n有交易，其實同坐巴士去景點差唔多價錢，甚至仲平，仲要唔使就班次<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身有車</blockquote><br />\n巴打識日文？？</blockquote><br />\n上網撳定就得<br />\n日本租車公司多數有網上租車<br />\n唔駛識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4faa68279f0306a1623fce0eab64ce017339bc","tid":241101,"uid":84116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完桂林返，深圳出發，4日揸左2000公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神州定一嗨租車？？租邊架？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有興趣係大陸租車，有冇多d詳情講下<br />\n<br />\n利申1：就黎甩p<br />\n利申2：係香港冇乜揸車經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cbe40d712c1382338671e9581806ee245bf318","tid":241101,"uid":20048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家去日本慣左坐JR，<br />\n之後到某個市就租一日車8am-8pm，2-3000 yen有交易，其實同坐巴士去景點差唔多價錢，甚至仲平，仲要唔使就班次<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身有車</blockquote><br />\n巴打識日文？？</blockquote><br />\n上網撳定就得<br />\n日本租車公司多數有網上租車<br />\n唔駛識日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n租咩車可以咁平？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4e3b3147335f25335be6a290ce334ed28d32df","tid":241101,"uid":84078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完桂林返，深圳出發，4日揸左2000公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神州定一嗨租車？？租邊架？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一嗨，好多新車，租左架速派，幾好揸可以上到230，最重要全部都掛緊臨時牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22b577a1270613cd16f4477e6973e1311658718","tid":241101,"uid":84078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blo