大陸租車，有冇多d詳情講下<br />\n<br />\n利申1：就黎甩p<br />\n利申2：係香港冇乜揸車經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我建議甩P後<br />\n先轉番個大陸牌<br />\n跟住搵個大陸陪駕係大陸揸下<br />\n架車同你學車個d車一樣，陪駕可剎車。<br />\n之前搵個陪駕，一堂兩個鐘兩百蚊人仔"},{"pid":"404cbddbdcacb0ae782ddbcd190e7e2c7cc6a3b3","tid":241101,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完桂林返，深圳出發，4日揸左2000公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神州定一嗨租車？？租邊架？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一嗨，好多新車，租左架速派，幾好揸可以上到230，最重要全部都掛緊臨時牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我租開雪鐵龍愛麗舍，大眾朗逸d cheap車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次租別克昂科拉suv試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0649140c22cb73c953bf51da0f84fbfae11e9a1a","tid":241101,"uid":13358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T03:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩去完桂林返，深圳出發，4日揸左2000公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神州定一嗨租車？？租邊架？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一嗨，好多新車，租左架速派，幾好揸可以上到230，最重要全部都掛緊臨時牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我租開雪鐵龍愛麗舍，大眾朗逸d cheap車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次租別克昂科拉suv試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都鐘意試唔同既車<br />\n不過有時同行d人會嫌貴, 咁就又要租最cheap"},{"pid":"bffdb3ec74621771b72dce57274d98e5d19ccc25","tid":241101,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T04:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor